==Overview==
The Hyperion is widely regarded as the best ship in the [[M6+]] class. Fast, powerful, well defended and with a quick turn rate for its class, it is capable of taking a fight to any opponent, from [[M5|scouts]] to [[M2|destroyers]]. On top of its impressive combat capabilities, it is the only corvette in the [[X-universe]] to have the function to dock and launch two [[:Category:Fighters|fighter class]] ships - this gives this ship the versitility to operate in many situations. However, it is not available to buy, and must be [[Bigship Boarding|''acquired'']] by other means.

==Background==
The Hyperion was first introduced as a prototype [[M7]] class yacht for the [[Paranid]] where it was significantly larger and more powerful. Its classification has changed over time to a cheaper and more compact [[M6+]], but remains a rather unique vessel, even after it started to be produced in larger numbers.

==Physical Characteristics==
The Hyperion's sleek lines demonstrate typical Paranid design. It has a small profile from both forward and the side and the upper profile is not particularly large either.

== Combat ==
The Hyperion has eight main guns, two side turrets that can fire forwards as well as having a huge angular range, and two rear three gun mount turrets. It can be equipped with all of the common corvette weapons in the main battery; [[High Energy Plasma Thrower|HEPT]], [[Concussion_Impulse_Generator|CIG]], [[Energy_Bolt_Chaingun|EBC]], [[Pulsed_Beam_Emitter|PBE]], [[Ion Shard Railgun|ISR]] and [[Plasma_Burst_Generator|PBG]] as well as the Paranid's own flak weapon, the [[Fragmentation Bomb Launcher]]. As such, it can be equipped with specialist weapons for every combat role. 

Choice in the forward turrets is more restricted, with only the HEPT, EBC and FBL as options unless the more ubiquitous [[Particle Accelerator Cannon|PAC]], which can be mounted in all slots and is an old but very effective weapon, is used.

The rear turrets are most restricted of all; only the FBL, IRE, and PAC can be mounted here.

Although it does not mount any heavy guns, it is the only [[Commonwealth]] vessel capable of launching the immensely potent [[Wraith Missile]] at a target, and also the only one capable of matching the Wraith's maximum speed (170 m/s), so that many can be launched on top of the others if the target is far enough. This overwhelms any defenses.

The Hyperion's shields are among the strongest of all M6s at 1GJ, allowing it to take a massive amount of punishment before succumbing.

